node.text:
When @danmagro asks for a #pridepour contribution in honor of #pridemonth, he gets a #pridepour....and also a #rainbow chicken perch that he def did NOT ask for.
-
I submit: The Rainbow-jito, which is a layered, tropical, melon-y twist on a #mojito...and it's full of #rum-soaked fruit. You can find the recipe by following the link in my profile.
-
But the point of #pridepour isn't just about making pretty rainbow drinks, it's about showing support and love for our LGTBQ+ loved ones, and hopefully raising some funds for organizations that benefit the LGTBQ+ community.
-
As such, we have brought back our Pride Rooster t-shirt (it's now available in a tank, too), over on #shopDWC (link in profile). 100% of profits from the sale of each shirt will be donated to @trevorproject in support of their efforts to provide real-time crisis intervention for LGTBQ+ youth.
-
Sending virtual love, drinks, and chicken joy to my LGTBQ+ friends this month and every month. ❤️🌈🍹🐓
#drinkingwithchickens 
.
.

.
